{"tid":2450354,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"【電動車普及路線圖】 擬最遲2035年停止新登記燃油車","createTime":"2021-03-17T10:21:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T16:23:47.000Z","uid":310850,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e6df88fc22a89922e814a35a1b13d8e5fb216fb4","tid":2450354,"uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T10:21:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zn4E62W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZn4E62W.png&h=a3f3230c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/4368971639877525/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F715486135226112%2Fposts%2F4368971639877525%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT96RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=faa97238\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/4368971639877525/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n（香港電台）環境局公布電動車普及化路線圖，包含6個範疇，提出2035年或以前停止新登記燃油私家車，包括混合動力車；提高一換一計劃下，電動私家車的首次登記稅寬減至約28萬7500元，並延長計劃至2024年3月。<br />\n<br />\n另外，政府會推動試驗各種電動公共交通及商用車，包括單層巴士、的士、雙層巴士、公共小巴等，其中單層巴士和公共小巴方面會分別投入1億8000萬元及8000萬元。<br />\n<br />\n就充電網絡方面，當局研究要求未來新建私人樓宇停車位，必須配備充電基建；物色地點建立快速充電網絡，研究轉型加油站；以及計劃在2025年公共充電設施多於5000個。<br />\n<br />\n環境局局長黃錦星表示，目標是2050年前達致車輛零排放，配合香港2050年前碳中和的目標。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台 #RTHK #港台電視31 #十點半新聞天地 #電動車 #燃油車"},{"pid":"6fe7fc53939a49d116df3d57cf709cd7e57c8b67","tid":2450354,"uid":137038,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T10:25:05.000Z","msg":"想知的士可以點玩電動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔使做生意？<br />\n小巴又係"},{"pid":"37fa8dc32982db24ca8ad5cbf77a3b1ac678d4f6","tid":2450354,"uid":224533,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T10:27:36.000Z","msg":"第一步停汽油車<br />\n第二步禁止買Tesla 只准買痕遲 BYD"},{"pid":"f7c0a4a2b8b8dfe1957309197d89d6cf79e6ce6b","tid":2450354,"uid":84013,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T10:29:25.000Z","msg":"笑死，強推電動<br />\n15萬叉電位夠邊個用<br />\n<br />\n到時就係狂加稅加牌費<br />\n迫人搭巴士地鐵<br />\n有錢人（包括大陸）、高官先比用"},{"pid":"e1b872d3d9abb64cbc8a6bb4b7442cf782c1be8a","tid":2450354,"uid":84013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T10:30:28.000Z","msg":"hybrid 車都唔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重唔係想利益輸送比byd"},{"pid":"a1cbbb2b620c5f56c6292da9ffc122d03769d648","tid":2450354,"uid":12609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6fe7fc53939a49d116df3d57cf709cd7e57c8b67","tid":2450354,"uid":137038,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T10:25:05.000Z","msg":"想知的士可以點玩電動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔使做生意？<br />\n小巴又係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T10:31:00.000Z","msg":"冇話要的士小巴電動化喎"},{"pid":"8a4bf5730a93cb4baba2a9ee9b68f315da1057ea","tid":2450354,"uid":299830,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T10:34:18.000Z","msg":"黃大仙既叉電位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.enb.gov.hk/sites/default/files/pdf/EV_roadmap_chi.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.enb.gov.hk%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fpdf%2FEV_roadmap_chi.pdf&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT96RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=25a06150\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.enb.gov.hk/sites/default/files/pdf/EV_roadmap_chi.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"229ca9f26b7c20e3e603aa5cd8c1997a8f432c04","tid":2450354,"uid":137038,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1cbbb2b620c5f56c6292da9ffc122d03769d648","tid":2450354,"uid":12609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6fe7fc53939a49d116df3d57cf709cd7e57c8b67","tid":2450354,"uid":137038,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"rep